episodes.content: AgentNet is a multi-agent reasoning platform with policy governance
P2 phase introduces vector store integration and tool registry
Memory system has three layers: short-term, episodic, and semantic
Tools are executed with rate limiting and authentication
Semantic memory uses vector similarity for content retrieval
